article.headline: Evee puts up 28 in Rice's 82-56 win against Prairie View A&M

images.name: Prairie View A&M Panthers vs. Rice Owls: Full Highlights
images.caption: Prairie View A&M Panthers vs. Rice Owls: Full Highlights

article.linkText: Evee puts up 28 in Rice's 82-56 win against Prairie View A&M
article.story: HOUSTON -- — Travis Evee's 28 points helped Rice defeat Prairie View A&M 82-56 on Wednesday night. Evee added five rebounds for the Owls (6-6). Mekhi Mason scored 14 points while shooting 6 for 11, including 2 for 4 from beyond the arc, and added three blocks. Anthony Selden added 11 points. Max Fiedler grabbed 14 rebounds to go with six points. Javontae Hopkins led the Panthers (5-6) in scoring, finishing with 16 points. Kevin McGaskey and Nick Gazelas finished with 11 points apiece. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
